# MERN Cab Rental Platform - Complete Development Guide

## 1. Project Overview

A full-featured ride-sharing and vehicle rental platform supporting:
- Self-driving car rentals (hourly/daily rates)
- Driver-operated rentals (distance/time-based pricing)
- Two-wheelers (bikes, scooters)
- Real-time vehicle tracking
- User/Driver/Owner registration and management
- Payment processing
- Rating and review system

---

## 2. Technology Stack

### Frontend (React)
- **React** - Core framework
- **Redux Toolkit** - State management
- **React Router** - Navigation
- **Axios** - API calls
- **Mapbox/Google Maps** - Real-time tracking, route planning
- **Socket.io-client** - Real-time communication
- **Stripe/Razorpay SDK** - Payment processing
- **Formik + Yup** - Form validation
- **Tailwind CSS** or **Material-UI** - Styling

### Backend (Node.js + Express)
- **Express.js** - Web framework
- **MongoDB** - NoSQL database
- **Mongoose** - ODM for MongoDB
- **Socket.io** - Real-time WebSocket communication
- **JWT** - Authentication tokens
- **Multer** - File uploads (vehicle documents, photos)
- **Stripe/Razorpay API** - Payment processing
- **Nodemailer** - Email notifications
- **Twilio** - SMS notifications
- **Google Maps API** - Distance, duration, directions
- **PM2** - Process management

### Database (MongoDB)
- Collections: Users, Drivers, Vehicles, Bookings, Payments, Reviews, Tracking

