## 4. Core Features Implementation

### 4.1 Authentication & Authorization
- JWT-based authentication
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- Email/SMS verification
- Two-factor authentication (optional)
- Social login (Google, Facebook)

### 4.2 User Management
- Registration with KYC verification
- Profile management
- Wallet system (prepaid balance)
- Referral system
- Emergency contacts

### 4.3 Vehicle Management
- Vehicle listing with image upload
- Document verification
- Real-time availability
- Multi-language support for vehicle descriptions

### 4.4 Booking System
- Search vehicles by location, type, availability
- Dynamic pricing (base fare + distance + time + surge)
- Booking cancellation with refund policy
- Scheduled bookings (future rides)
- Waitlist for unavailable vehicles

### 4.5 Real-Time Tracking
- WebSocket-based live tracking
- GPS location updates from vehicle (mobile app with GPS)
- Route visualization on map
- ETA calculation
- Geofencing alerts

### 4.6 Driver Features
- Driver registration with verification
- Available/unavailable status
- Earnings dashboard
- Weekly/monthly statements
- Withdrawal management
- Document renewal alerts

### 4.7 Payment System
- Multiple payment methods (card, wallet, UPI, etc.)
- Surge pricing during peak hours
- Split fare option
- Coupon/promo code system
- Invoice generation

### 4.8 Rating & Reviews
- Bidirectional rating (customer rates driver/vehicle, vice versa)
- Detailed review comments
- Photo uploads with reviews
- Review moderation system

