## 6. Key Implementation Steps

### Phase 1: Foundation (Weeks 1-2)
- Set up MongoDB and connect with Mongoose
- Create user authentication system (signup, login, JWT)
- Implement role-based access control
- Set up basic API endpoints for users

### Phase 2: Vehicle Management (Weeks 3-4)
- Create vehicle listing system
- Implement file upload for documents and images
- Build vehicle search/filter functionality
- Create location-based queries using geospatial indexing

### Phase 3: Booking System (Weeks 5-6)
- Create booking model and endpoints
- Implement dynamic pricing calculation
- Build booking workflow (request → confirm → pickup → complete)
- Add cancellation and refund logic

### Phase 4: Real-Time Features (Weeks 7-8)
- Set up Socket.io for real-time tracking
- Implement GPS location updates
- Build live tracking map on frontend
- Add real-time notifications

### Phase 5: Payment Integration (Weeks 9-10)
- Integrate Stripe/Razorpay
- Implement multiple payment methods
- Build payment failure handling
- Create invoice system

### Phase 6: Driver Features (Weeks 11-12)
- Create driver registration and verification
- Build driver dashboard
- Implement earnings tracking
- Add withdrawal system

### Phase 7: Reviews & Ratings (Weeks 13)
- Create bidirectional rating system
- Implement review moderation
- Add photo uploads with reviews

### Phase 8: Testing & Optimization (Weeks 14-16)
- Write unit and integration tests
- Performance optimization
- Security audit
- Deployment to cloud (AWS/Heroku/DigitalOcean)

