## 10. Getting Started

### Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend
npm init -y
npm install express mongoose dotenv cors bcryptjs jsonwebtoken socket.io stripe multer
npm install --save-dev nodemon

# Create .env file with:
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_uri
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=your_stripe_key
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_key
```

### Frontend Setup
```bash
npm create vite@latest frontend -- --template react
cd frontend
npm install redux @reduxjs/toolkit react-router-dom axios socket.io-client
npm install @mapbox/mapbox-gl stripe react-stripe-js
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
```

